Definition eqb (a b : byte) : bool
  := let '(a0, (a1, (a2, (a3, (a4, (a5, (a6, a7))))))) := to_bits a in
     let '(b0, (b1, (b2, (b3, (b4, (b5, (b6, b7))))))) := to_bits b in
     (Bool.eqb a0 b0 && Bool.eqb a1 b1 && Bool.eqb a2 b2 && Bool.eqb a3 b3 &&
          Bool.eqb a4 b4 && Bool.eqb a5 b5 && Bool.eqb a6 b6 && Bool.eqb a7 b7)%bool.
Lemma byte_dec_lb x y : x = y -> eqb x y = true.
intro; subst y; destruct x; reflexivity.
Lemma byte_dec_bl x y (H : eqb x y = true) : x = y.

goals.conclusion:
(let
 '(a0, (a1, (a2, (a3, (a4, (a5, (a6, a7))))))) :=
  to_bits x in
  let
  '(b0, (b1, (b2, (b3, (b4, (b5, (b6, b7))))))) :=
   to_bits y in
   (Bool.eqb a0 b0 && Bool.eqb a1 b1 && Bool.eqb a2 b2 &&
    Bool.eqb a3 b3 && Bool.eqb a4 b4 && Bool.eqb a5 b5 &&
    Bool.eqb a6 b6 && Bool.eqb a7 b7)%bool) = true ->
of_bits (to_bits x) = of_bits (to_bits y)

contents: generalize (to_bits x) (to_bits y); clear x y; intros x y H.

(let

  x in
  let
  '(b0, (b1, (b2, (b3, (b4, (b5, (b6, b7))))))) :=
   y in
   (Bool.eqb a0 b0 && Bool.eqb a1 b1 &&
    Bool.eqb a2 b2 && Bool.eqb a3 b3 &&
    Bool.eqb a4 b4 && Bool.eqb a5 b5 &&
    Bool.eqb a6 b6 && Bool.eqb a7 b7)%bool) = true
